DNA strand displacement and TdT-Mediated DNA extension for swift, convenient, 
and quantitative evaluation of sperm DNA integrity and its clinical 
implications.

Yan B(1), Fan H(2), Ji H(3), Li S(3), Hu H(2), Gu X(4), Jia S(5), Liu Y(6), Guo 
J(6), Yang Z(6), Zhou L(6), Xiao X(7), Li L(8), Mao Z(9).

Author information:
